{
  "message": "Add react-tweet, react-force-graph, sql.js, and d3 dependencies\n\nNew runtime deps:\n- react-tweet v3.3.0: Renders real X/Twitter embeds with full media\n  (images, video, quoted tweets) instead of static text cards\n- react-force-graph v1.45.1: D3-force powered graph visualization\n  for the beads dependency viewer\n- sql.js v1.12.0: In-browser SQLite for reading beads database files\n\nNew dev deps:\n- d3 v7.9.0 + @types/d3: Graph layout algorithms and data joins\n- @types/sql.js v1.4.9: TypeScript definitions for sql.js\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
